However, you can also treat yourself to microcapsules that spread fresh forest or lavender scent while sleeping.
Here, too, there is a difference between man and woman.
While men use a "cooler" plant extract from birch leaves so that the mattress cover can absorb heat and cool the body, the covers for women have a "warming" effect.
Extracts from red bell peppers stimulate blood circulation, so the weaker sex warms up comfortably when sleeping.
What about today’s favorites?
Cold foam mattresses (it has larger pores with destroyed cell structure and is therefore more breathable than commercially available polyurethane and also much more flexible).
By combining the various stiffness (hardness) of cold foams and visco foams, multi-zone mattresses are created that know exactly where the head, hip and heels are located.
For a high-quality mattress, however, you have 7000 crowns and more to cover.
However, health mattresses are usually charged with lower VAT because they are considered medical aids.
Gumotex was the first Czech company to benefit from this advantage.
You can see, saving on the mattress and on the rust is not so easy.
Occasionally there are special offers from manufacturers and dealers who offer two mattresses at the price of one.
For example, the Magniflex brand offers the mattress Duofreeze with visco foam memory quilted in the reference for 11,990 CZK.
The second one is given for free.
It was the Tempur material that initiated the era of viscoelastic foams with open cell structure and high density at almost cosmic pace.
No wonder they were developed for NASA, because the astronauts are exposed to enormous overloads at the launches.
Tempur becomes soft in heat, in cool environment it in turn solidifies.
In this way, it adapts perfectly to the human body and distributes the body pressure in an optimal way.
It is therefore not only ideal for preventing pressure burn, but generally increases sleep comfort.
However, viscoelastic foams are used not only in mattresses, but also in other health products, such as special foot pads, which are intended to provide relief to the legs and vessels.
For example, local manufacturers use the foams Eucatherm C, Twinsaver or similar products.
