The reform of the Organic Law on Congress will introduce the two-party system, they complain.
The 60th legislature had just begun, and an opposition bloc, led by the members of the PRD, PT, Convergencia and Jesús Manuel Patrón Montalvo, had already been installed, which presented itself as an independent. The four questioned the entry of the 'two-party system' into the chamber.
